News.Title: Delaplex Forms Strategic Partnership With California IT Firm to Enhance Data Management Solutions
News.Summary: Delaplex has entered into a strategic partnership with a global IT firm based in California. The collaboration aims to improve data management solutions and expand market presence by combining technological expertise with sales capabilities.

News.Title: Delaplex Empanelled as National System Integrator for BSNL
News.Summary: Delaplex, a company with a market capitalization of 142 crore rupees, has been empanelled as a system integrator at the national level for Bharat Sanchar Nigam Limited (BSNL), India's state-owned telecommunications service provider.
